Yes, he is beautiful, Heidi.

22
00:01:35,530 --> 00:01:37,530
Will you bring him to me?

23
00:01:42,906 --> 00:01:48,346
Wait, Butterfly! I'll catch you!

24
00:01:49,358 --> 00:01:50,358
Ouch!

25
00:01:53,358 --> 00:01:54,358
Are you from the city?

26
00:01:54,358 --> 00:01:55,358
Yes!

27
00:01:56,358 --> 00:01:57,358
That's why we're marking you!

28
00:01:57,358 --> 00:01:58,358
And how!

29
00:01:59,358 --> 00:02:02,358
If you thought you could do it better, then go ahead!

30
00:02:03,358 --> 00:02:04,358
Come on!

31
00:02:04,358 --> 00:02:05,358
Let's go!

32
00:02:08,358 --> 00:02:10,358
Don't be so rude!

33
00:02:10,358 --> 00:02:12,358
You can't just stand on your feet like that!

34
00:02:12,358 --> 00:02:14,358
He flew over there!

35
00:02:18,358 --> 00:02:19,358
I caught him!

36
00:02:25,358 --> 00:02:26,358
Now I'll catch him!

37
00:02:26,358 --> 00:02:27,358
Careful!

38
00:02:29,358 --> 00:02:31,358
But be careful with him!

39
00:02:31,358 --> 00:02:32,358
Don't hurt him!

40
00:02:32,358 --> 00:02:34,358
Butterflies have sensitive wings!

41
00:02:35,358 --> 00:02:36,358
There?

42
00:02:36,358 --> 00:02:37,358
No!

43
