No!

44
00:02:38,358 --> 00:02:39,358
Over there!

45
00:02:43,358 --> 00:02:44,358
Hang on!

46
00:02:44,358 --> 00:02:45,358
I'll catch him!

47
00:02:50,358 --> 00:02:51,358
Now!

48
00:02:52,358 --> 00:02:54,358
Oh, nothing again!

49
00:02:54,358 --> 00:02:56,358
Don't worry, I can save you!

50
00:02:56,358 --> 00:02:57,358
I can catch him!

51
00:02:57,358 --> 00:02:58,358
I'll catch him!

52
00:03:12,358 --> 00:03:16,038
We did it! We did it! We got the butterfly!

53
00:03:16,092 --> 00:03:18,092
There you have it.

54
00:03:18,092 --> 00:03:20,092
Thank you.

55
00:03:20,092 --> 00:03:22,092
I've never seen you here before.

56
00:03:22,092 --> 00:03:24,092
We're only here this afternoon.

57
00:03:24,092 --> 00:03:26,092
But you must be quite rich.

58
00:03:26,092 --> 00:03:28,092
I saw how you arrived.

59
00:03:28,092 --> 00:03:30,092
You rarely see such a big carriage here.

60
00:03:30,092 --> 00:03:32,092
It doesn't belong to me.

61
00:03:32,092 --> 00:03:34,092
The carriage belongs to Clara's father.

62
00:03:36,092 --> 00:03:38,092
Why is she sitting in the wheelchair?

63
00:03:38,092 --> 00:03:40,092
What's wrong with her?

64
00:03:40,092 --> 00:03:42,092
Clara can't walk.

65
00:03:46,092 --> 00:03:48,092
Clara!

66
00:03:48,092 --> 00:03:50,092
We caught the butterfly.

67
00:03:50,092 --> 00:03:52,092
The two boys helped us.

68
00:03:57,052 --> 00:03:58,812
Come on, Klaus, let's go.

69
00:03:58,812 --> 00:03:59,812
Goodbye.

70
00:03:59,812 --> 00:04:00,812
It's okay.

71
00:04:00,812 --> 00:04:01,812
Goodbye, girl.

72
00:04:01,812 --> 00:04:02,812
Maybe we'll see you again.

73
00:04:02,812 --> 00:04:03,812
Goodbye.

74
00:04:03,812 --> 00:04:04,812
Klara!

75
00:04:04,812 --> 00:04:05,812
It's a pretty butterfly.

76
00:04:05,812 --> 00:04:06,812
You'll like it too.

77
00:04:06,812 --> 00:04:07,812
I have it in my hands here.

78
00:04:07,812 --> 00:04:08,812
Now I don't want to see it anymore.

79
00:04:08,812 --> 00:04:09,812
But why all of a sudden?

80
00:04:09,812 --> 00:04:10,812
The two boys and I have put so much effort into it.

81
00:04:10,812 --> 00:04:11,812
That's what it is.

82
00:04:11,812 --> 00:04:12,812
You have put so much effort into it and I have to sit here in this stupid
wheelchair.

83
00:04:12,812 --> 00:04:13,812
Now you're sad.

84
